TopicTitle: Part missing on load of vessel

Articles.Content:
Hi, KSP community

Can you help me ?

I have (re)installed KSP recently.

I had created most vessels with previous KSP versions (1.8.x)

With 1.12.5 version, when I would like load vessels, I have an error: "Vessel xxx is missing part xxx"

The missing parts are Clydesdale and LiquidEngine2. But it seems to me that those are vanilla parts ?!
 

Edited March 10, 2023 by sarigue
Screenshot

Hum... 

"Clydesdale" part exists in Squad\Parts\Engine\solidBoosterS2-33\, but KSP doesn't find it ?! 

And I found "liquidEngine2-2" in Squad\zDeprecated\Parts\Engine\liquidEnginePoodle_v1\... but KSP doesn't find it ?!
